    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition, and prospective buyers will be pleased with what they find. The exterior is flawless \u2014 paint retains its deep, original luster with absolutely no scratches, dents, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. All trim, glass, and seals are in perfect order. The interior is equally pristine: seats, carpeting, headliner, and all surfaces show zero wear, staining, or fading, looking and smelling as though the car just rolled off the showroom floor. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent working order \u2014 the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems (brakes, suspension, transmission, HVAC, electronics) function perfectly with no warning lights, unusual noises, or deferred maintenance. Service records are up to date, and there are no known issues whatsoever. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that truly needs nothing \u2014 it is ready to drive and enjoy from day one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we are committed to full transparency with every potential buyer. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a good shine with only minor surface scratches and small blemishes consistent with normal use. There are no significant rust issues, though a close inspection may reveal light wear on edges and door jambs. The interior is clean and functional; upholstery shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and high-touch areas, but there are no tears or major stains. All primary controls, windows, and electronics operate as expected. Under the hood, the engine starts reliably and runs smoothly \u2014 service records indicate regular oil changes and routine maintenance have been kept up. The tires have decent tread remaining, and the brakes feel responsive. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been used and shows it honestly, but is far from a project car. A great choice for a buyer seeking reliable daily transportation without paying a premium for showroom-perfect condition.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a clear, honest picture of what you're getting. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 expect noticeable scratches, some dents, and areas where the paint has faded or chipped. The interior is functional but shows its age with worn upholstery, scuffs on trim panels, and general signs of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it is not without its quirks \u2014 there may be minor issues that a buyer should be prepared to address, and we recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic. This is not a mint or showroom-quality vehicle, but it is a serviceable car for a buyer who understands its condition and is looking for basic, everyday transportation at a fair price. What you see is what you get \u2014 no hidden surprises.",
